@mref{orderless} bestimmt.

@c For undeclared arrays, array functions, and subscripted functions, the 
@c elements correspond to the index values returned by @code{arrayinfo}.

F@"ur undeklarierte Arrays, Array-Funktionen und indizierte Funktionen werden
die Elemente in der Reihenfolge wie von der Funktion 
@mref{arrayinfo} zur@"uckgegeben.

@c Unbound elements of declared general arrays (that is, not @code{fixnum} and 
@c not @code{flonum}) are returned as @code{#####}. Unbound elements of declared
@c @code{fixnum} or @code{flonum} arrays are returned as 0 or 0.0, respectively.
@c Unbound elements of undeclared arrays, array functions, and subscripted 
